<div class="key-services">
  <section class="daily-savings" id="daily-savings">
    <div class="heading container">
      <h2>Daily Savings</h2>
      <p>Start saving smarter today</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p class="container">
        One of the best ways to save money is to set a goal. Start by thinking
        about what you might want to save for - both in the short term (one to
        three years) and the long term (four or more years). Then estimate how
